<lb ed="C I" n="0119a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 47</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>朱永隆七十人等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a01"/><p id="pI01p0119a0101">夫鏡日輝玄。<note n="0119001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30318;＝&CB30397;【史】</note><app n="0119001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app>妙識於淨海。澄波洰<note n="0119002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30319;＝壑【史】</note><app n="0119002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30319;</rdg></app>。運境目於生源。是以八相同紛。闢重<note n="0119003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30285;＝關【史】</note><app n="0119003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30285;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a02"/>於幽夜。三輪<note n="0119004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00150;＝昺【史】</note><app n="0119004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00150;</rdg></app>轍。闡神機於正路。<note n="0119005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11576;＝使【史】</note><app n="0119005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">使</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11576;</rdg></app>遊子歸衢。輕車<note n="0119006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30320;＝迅【史】</note><app n="0119006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30320;</rdg></app>駕。炎宅止<note n="0119007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02690;＝焚【史】</note><app n="0119007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02690;</rdg></app>。冰池攸淥。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a03"/>故能振馨風於沖漠之野。擊玉磬於<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>聲之<note n="0119008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30321;＝鄉【史】</note><app n="0119008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鄉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30321;</rdg></app>。遂大鵬奮霄。龍<note n="0119009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30322;＝翔【史】</note><app n="0119009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30322;</rdg></app><note n="0119010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【史】</note><app n="0119010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>湊。六合<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雲</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a04"/>翻。十方斯集。金言演暢。豪光九<note n="0119011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30334;＝照【史】</note><app n="0119011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30334;</rdg></app>。法界融蕩。瓊<note n="0119012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30323;＝華【史】</note><app n="0119012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30323;</rdg></app>七瑩。乃塵沙涉靜浪之舟。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a05"/>形蒙麾棹之緣。於是騰超彼<note n="0119013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30324;＝岸【史】</note><app n="0119013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30324;</rdg></app>。濟度<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>崖。必以朝露易<note n="0119014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30325;＝晞【史】</note><app n="0119014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">晞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30325;</rdg></app>。浮霜難固。提河早流。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a06"/>皓林促<note n="0119015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30326;＝變【史】</note><app n="0119015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">變</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30326;</rdg></app>。隱影靈遷。圓明息曜。三界悲動。四生<note n="0119016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30327;＝號【史】</note><app n="0119016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">號</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30327;</rdg></app>慕。賢徒泣血。能言瀝地。大
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a07"/>聖垂慈。敷十二以流導。悲愍將來。布舍利以昌&CB00528;。故優填鐫姿。育王建塔。所在
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a08"/>模容。流芳万國。自尒暨今。邁餘千載。寺有魏大法師故沙門都法恩。起妙因於
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a09"/>初心。建淨業於<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>始。故童年去或。高步<note n="0119017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09158;＝緇【史】</note><app n="0119017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09158;</rdg></app>門。逍遙法菀。矯志松蘭。縕思玄蹤。物
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a10"/>我俱懷。遂捨衣&CB00425;之餘。採石名山。訪巧求能。願雕真容。但<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常驚逝。峰&CB00195;激速。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a11"/>創福未周。奄從物化。門徒<note n="0119018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00079;＝嗥【史】</note><app n="0119018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嗥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00079;</rdg></app>戀。精感<note n="0119019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02793;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0119019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app><note n="0119020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06457;＝篤【史】</note><app n="0119020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">篤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06457;</rdg></app>。又弟子法度。戒行冰朗。智超空有。仰
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a12"/>稟師則。磬志忠誠。更崇妍瑑。妙<note n="0119021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30329;＝鏤【史】</note><app n="0119021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鏤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30329;</rdg></app>金顏。釋迦怡怡。若兜率之趣琦殿。<note n="0119022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0119022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app>勒昂昂。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a13"/>狀龍華之&CB30397;三會。多寶同坐。事等湧出。飛堪&CB00297;虛。<note n="0119023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30330;＝旋【史】</note><app n="0119023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30330;</rdg></app>瓔<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">反</unclear>入。維摩權形。嘿言於
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a14"/>方丈。文殊十辭。表問疾於平等。菩薩諸天。簫瑟芙麗。金剛密跡。獻目楊<note n="0119024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02098;＝階【史】</note><app n="0119024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">階</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02098;</rdg></app>。飾像
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a15"/>雖訖。嵩塔未備。而度曉夕慇。<note n="0119025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30331;＝觀【史】</note><app n="0119025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">觀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30331;</rdg></app>成神宇。不謂暴疾所鐘。潛魂深夜。致使營　圖
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a16"/>中癈。為山止匱。復有此寺上坐僧惠。寺主法合。並湛潔內融。皎志方外。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">持</unclear>四<note n="0119026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30332;＝攝【史】</note><app n="0119026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">攝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30332;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a17"/>於匈衿。騁七<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臠</unclear>於神膺。洞博群經。智遊<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app><note n="0119027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01002;＝礙【史】</note><app n="0119027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">礙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01002;</rdg></app>。<note n="0119028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30746;＝緇【史】</note><app n="0119028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30746;</rdg></app>素同遵。歸依各流。又邑主朱永
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a18"/>隆。唐豐七十人等。各槃根蘭冑。挺茂華芳。&CB05007;葩槐蕀。籍潤斯遠。發悟自天。契達
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a19"/>幽旨。普相率厲。敦崇邑義。以其處也。碧地流泉。勢俠中都。金豪光泗。鬱澤新鮮。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a20"/>蓊林翠柏。璨然在目。布寶求園。謂莫斯過。遂採棟雲臺。代木方巖。班匠麗功。造
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a21"/>天宮一<note n="0119029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00100;＝區【史】</note><app n="0119029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00100;</rdg></app>。巍巍赫<note n="0119030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30333;＝奕【史】</note><app n="0119030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30333;</rdg></app>。媚若祇桓。堂堂<app source="0119004" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00150;</rdg></app>煥。婉踰神塔。迷者一闞。則洗或於先源。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a22"/>慧者暫睹。則感悟於後際。可謂福潤含生。祚隆<app source="0119022" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app><note n="0119031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03567;＝劫【史】</note><app n="0119031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03567;</rdg></app>。酬功報德。鐫石遐芳。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a23"/>其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a24"/>皎皎淨性。洸洸境日。湛波<app source="0119001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app>旭。騰源曜質。現託王宮。曠周遐悉。鸞翔□翥。法□
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a25"/>斯一。　大音唱諭。名義弗違。淨光電掃。輕舟返飛。浮&CB00195;靜霧。赫日□□。致遷景
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a26"/>覺。人天<note n="0119032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02508;＝罔【史】</note><app n="0119032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02508;</rdg></app>歸。　三千號慟。沖影潛空。愍彼長迷。敷此幽綜。爰有哲士。紹隆聖蹤。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a27"/>彫&CB00216;鐫像。以表靈容。　英信等悟。磬寶脩圖。福延<app source="0119022" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app><app source="0119031" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03567;</rdg></app>。鏡水非<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">虛</unclear>。善潤　皇家。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a28"/>祚融唐虞。蠢尒同津。咸契凝如。
<lb ed="C I" n="0119a29"/>　　　　　大魏武定三年歲次乙丑七月戊寅朔十五日壬辰樹</p>
